<p>Hi <%= @user %>,</p>

<p>To reset your password, click the link below:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Reset password', edit_password_reset_url(@user, token: @token), class: "text-blue-500 underline" %></p>

<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>

<p>Thanks,</p>
<p>Your Manga Reader Team</p>
